Class IPojoFactory.RetryNameGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.felix.ipojo.IPojoFactory.RetryNameGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPojoFactory.NameGenerator
    Enclosing class:
    IPojoFactory

    public static class IPojoFactory.RetryNameGenerator
extends Object
implements IPojoFactory.NameGenerator
    This generator implements a retry naming strategy. It uses a delegate IPojoFactory.NameGenerator, and call it in sequence until an unused value is found.
